This paper deals with decision-making and optimization, which are common topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses multiagent systems (cs.MA) and control systems (cs.SY) in the context of sequential decision-making. Finally, the paper uses mathematical models and algorithms, which are relevant to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
